\pard\f0\fs28   {\b 10. H. amblycalyx} Coust. & Gand.,{\i  Bull. Soc. Bot. Fr.}{\b  63}: 14 (1916). Like {\b 9} but with leaves in whorls of 4 and sepals with eglandular margin.{\i  Rocky places. E. Kriti.} Cr.
